## UI System (shadcn/ui)

- **Components location**: All primitives are under `web/components/ui`. Reuse before creating new primitives.
- **Design tokens**: Colors, radius, and CSS variables are defined in [globals.css](mdc:web/app/globals.css). Prefer tokens over hardcoded values.
- **Theme**: Use [theme-provider.tsx](mdc:web/components/theme-provider.tsx) to enable `next-themes` when needed. Add `'use client'` for client trees.
- **Variants & class names**: Use `class-variance-authority` in UI components and `cn` from [utils.ts](mdc:web/lib/utils.ts) to merge classes.
- **Icons**: Use `lucide-react`; keep icon size via Tailwind `h-* w-*` utilities.
- **Accessibility**: Follow Radix accessibility patterns; ensure focus styles and aria labels where relevant.

